American Diabetes Association Alert Day℠ Supporters

The American Diabetes Association is pleased to recognize our Alert Day Corporate Supporters for participating in the "Join the Million Challenge". These companies demonstrate their commitment to the diabetes epidemic and the importance of living an overall healthy lifestyle by supporting diabetes education and awareness. Together, we are working to help communities understand the risks of this devastating disease.

We want to say "thank you" to the following companies for their efforts in the fight against diabetes!

• AstraZeneca
• BD Medical-Diabetes Care
• Boar's Head Provisions Co., Inc.
• Boerhinger-Ingelheim Phamaceuticals
• Bristol-Myers Squibb
• Dignity® Memorial Network
• Catherines®
• GlaxoSmithKline (GSK)
• Gold's Gym
• HearPO

• Miracle-Ear®

• Nutrisystem®
• Quest Diagnostics®
• Rite Aid®
• Roche Diabetes Care
• T-Fal® Actifry®
• VSP® Vision Care
• Walmart
• WellPoint® Foundation

Stop Diabetes is the Association's movement to end the devastating toll that diabetes takes on the lives of millions of individuals and families across our nation. Join the Millions® in the Movement. Together we can Stop Diabetes®.
